videos.description: Penn State's Trace McSorley has miscommunication with a receiver and has his pass intercepted by USC's Iman Marshall.
videos.headline: Penn State throws an interception on first play from scrimmage

videos.description: Penn State's Trace McSorley has his pass tipped and intercepted by USC's Adoree' Jackson, McSorley's second interception of the first quarter.
videos.headline: Penn State's McSorley throws second interception of first quarter

videos.description: USC's Sam Darnold scrambles and throws to Deontay Burnett for a 26-yard touchdown in the first quarter against Penn State.
videos.headline: Darnold finds Burnett for USC's first touchdown

videos.description: USC confuses Penn State's defense with a reverse flea flicker. Jalen Greene catches the pass and weaves through traffic for a 28-yard gain.
videos.headline: USC gets tricky with reverse flea-flicker

videos.description: Penn State's Saquon Barkley rushes through a big hole and hits the end zone for a 24-yard touchdown in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Penn State responds with Barkley's 24-yard touchdown run

videos.description: USC's Sam Darnold completes a pass to Deontay Burnett who rushes away from the Penn State defense for a 32-yard gain.
videos.headline: Darnold connects with Burnett for a 32-yard gain

videos.description: Penn State's Trace McSorley throws to Chris Godwin who makes the catch and gets a foot inbounds for a 29-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Penn State's Godwin makes great grab in back of the end zone

videos.description: USC's Sam Darnold throws a jump ball for JuJu Smith-Schuster who leaps and comes down with the ball for a 36-yard gain.
videos.headline: Smith-Schuster leaps for big gain

videos.description: USC's Sam Darnold throws a quick pass to Darreus Rogers for a 3-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Darnold connects with Rogers to extend USC's lead

videos.description: USC's Sam Darnold finds Deontay Burnett on a short pass, going into the end zone for a 3-yard touchdown. The referees originally call for offensive pass interference, but it gets overturned because Burnett was behind the line of scrimmage.
videos.headline: Burnett's second TD upheld after penalty

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Burnett's second TD upheld after penalty) 2017/01/02

videos.description: Penn State's Trace McSorley throws behind Chris Godwin, but Godwin is able to make the catch with one hand for the first down.
videos.headline: Penn State's Godwin makes amazing one-handed grab

videos.description: Penn State's Mike Gesicki creates separation from a USC defender before making a full extension catch in the back of the end zone for an 11-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Penn State's Gesicki makes highlight-reel TD grab

videos.description: Both offenses are moving the ball in the opening half of the Rose Bowl Game with USC taking a 27-21 lead into halftime over Penn State.
videos.headline: USC leads Penn State at halftime of high-scoring Rose Bowl

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Rose Bowl USC-Penn State Halftime) 2017/01/02 ESHEET

videos.description: USC head coach Clay Helton breaks down the first 30 minutes of action at the Rose Bowl Game Presented by Northwestern Mutual.
videos.headline: Helton recaps exciting first half

videos.description: Penn State head coach James Franklin says his team is used to being in this situation at halftime and will makes adjustments for the second half.
videos.headline: Franklin says his team hates first halves

videos.description: Early in the third quarter, Penn State's Saquon Barkley makes a few USC defenders miss before speeding down the sideline for a 79-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Barkley scurries 79 yards for Penn State touchdown

videos.description: Penn State's Trace McSorley throws a deep ball that gets tipped by USC's Iman Marshall and caught by Chris Godwin who speeds away to score a 72-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Penn State's Godwin takes deflected pass 72 yards to the house

videos.description: USC's Sam Darnold throws a short pass that gets tipped in the air and intercepted by Penn State's Brandon Bell and returned 24 yards.
videos.headline: Penn State picks off Darnold early in the third quarter

videos.description: After a USC turnover, Penn State gets the ball deep in enemy territory, with quarterback Trace McSorley rushing into the end zone for a 3-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Penn State's McSorley keeps it himself for 3 yard touchdown

videos.description: USC's Sam Darnold throws to JuJu Smith-Schuster on a line for an 13-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Darnold connects with Smith-Schuster for 13-yard score

videos.description: Looking to gain momentum, USC's Sam Darnold rolls right then stops and throws to Taylor McNamara for the two-point conversion.
videos.headline: USC gets fancy with two-point conversion

videos.description: Penn State's Trace McSorley rolls right and throws to Saquon Barkley for a 7-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Barkley catches 7-yard touchdown to extend Penn State's lead

videos.description: USC's Adoree' Jackson returns the kickoff and gets tackled awkwardly, and needs to be helped off the field with a right leg injury.
videos.headline: USC's Adoree' Jackson helped off the field with apparent leg injury

videos.description: In the third quarter, USC's Cameron Smith gets assessed a targeting penalty for a hit on Penn State quarterback Trace McSorley. After review, the call is upheld and Smith leaves the game.
videos.headline: USC's Cameron Smith ejected for targeting

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (USC's Cameron Smith ejected for targeting) 2017/01/02

videos.description: USC'S Ronald Jones II takes the handoff and goes untouched into the end zone for a 3-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: USC inches closer with a Ronald Jones II 3-yard touchdown

videos.description: Trailing heading into the third quarter, Penn State's offense responds by scoring four touchdowns to take the lead over USC in the Rose Bowl.
videos.headline: Penn State's offense explodes in third quarter

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Penn State's offense explodes in third quarter) 2017/01/02 ESHEET

videos.description: USC stops Penn State on a late third-and-4 with Saquon Barkley getting tackled.
videos.headline: USC gets crucial stop on third-and-4

videos.description: Late in the fourth quarter, USC's Sam Darnold throws it to Deontay Burnett who leaps in the end zone for 27-yard touchdown, tying the game at 49.
videos.headline: USC ties game on Darnold's fifth touchdown pass en route to win

videos.description: Penn State's Trace McSorley throws a deep ball that gets intercepted by Leon McQuay III and returned 32 yards into Nittany Lions territory.
videos.headline: USC's McQuay III gets third Trojan interception in Rose Bowl

videos.description: With 5 seconds left in the fourth quarter, USC's Matt Boermeester makes a 46-yard field goal to give the Trojans a 52-49 victory over Penn State.
videos.headline: USC wins Rose Bowl on Boermeester's 46-yard field goal

videos.description: USC head coach Clay Helton discusses his feelings about his team's performance this season, capped off with a 52-49 win over Penn State.
videos.headline: Helton really proud of his team this season

videos.description: In one of the all-time greatest Rose Bowl Games, USC gets a field goal on the last play of the game to stun Penn State for a 52-49 victory.
videos.headline: USC wins classic Rose Bowl with FG at the buzzer

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Rose Bowl USC-Penn State Fulltime) 2017/01/02 ESHEET

videos.description: USC quarterback Sam Darnold breaks down his team's fourth-quarter comeback against Penn State, stressing that trust was a big factor.
videos.headline: Darnold says trust was the key for USC

videos.description: USC scores 17 unanswered points in the fourth quarter for an incredible comeback victory against Penn State in the Rose Bowl.
videos.headline: USC rallies to win amazing Rose Bowl

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Feature (USC rallies to win amazing Rose Bowl) 2017/01/03 ESHEET SCEU
